# Project Rules — Nexus Employee Portal

Tech stack: **Vite + React + TypeScript + TailwindCSS v4**

---

## Architecture

- Cấu trúc **feature-based** (`src/features/[name]/`)
- Mỗi feature chứa: `components/`, `hooks/`, `constants/`, `types/`
- `src/components/` — CHỈ shared/common UI components dùng chung trên ≥2 features
- `src/pages/` — Page-level components (route targets)
- `src/layouts/` — Layout wrappers (MainLayout, AuthLayout)
- `src/services/` — API service layer (axios instances, API functions)
- `src/stores/` — Zustand stores cho global/client state
- `src/types/` — Global TypeScript interfaces/types
- `src/config/` — App config, env variables
- `src/constants/` — Global constants, enums
- `src/hooks/` — Global custom hooks (shared across features)
- `src/utils/` — Utility/helper functions

```
src/
├── assets/
├── components/          # CHỈ shared UI (TopNav, Sidebar, ui/Button, ui/Modal...)
├── config/
│   └── env.ts           # Centralized env access
├── constants/
├── features/
│   └── [feature-name]/
│       ├── components/  # Feature-scoped components
│       ├── hooks/       # Feature-scoped hooks
│       ├── constants/
│       └── types/
├── hooks/               # Global custom hooks
├── layouts/
├── pages/
├── services/
│   ├── api.ts           # Axios instance + interceptors
│   └── [resource].service.ts
├── stores/
│   └── use[Name]Store.ts
├── types/
│   └── [resource].types.ts
├── utils/
├── App.tsx
├── main.tsx
└── index.css
```

